4. Products Made With the Engine

You retain ownership of any Products you create using the Engine,
excluding the Engine itself.

5. Royalty

(a) Royalty Obligation  
You agree to pay a royalty equal to **five percent (5%) of Gross Revenue**
generated from each Product that is developed using the Engine.

(b) Gross Revenue Definition  
"Gross Revenue" means all revenue actually received or receivable from a
Product, including but not limited to sales, in-app purchases,
subscriptions, advertising revenue, crowdfunding tied to the Product,
and any other form of monetization, **before** deducting any costs,
taxes, platform fees, or expenses.

(c) Reporting and Payment  
Royalty payments must be reported and paid on a quarterly basis, within
thirty (30) days after the end of each calendar quarter.

(d) Audit Rights  
The copyright holder reserves the right, upon reasonable notice, to audit
financial records solely for the purpose of verifying royalty payments.

(e) Waivers and Thresholds  
Any royalty-free thresholds, reduced rates, or waivers must be granted
explicitly in writing and are not implied by this License.

6. Contributions

Any feedback, suggestions, or source code contributions submitted to the
copyright holder may be used, modified, or incorporated into the Engine
without compensation or attribution.

7. Termination

This License is automatically terminated if you violate any of its
terms. Upon termination, you must immediately cease all use of the
Engine and destroy all copies in your possession.

